high_descs: Move across the room to the left side of the white table
Pick up the pen that is sitting on top of the table
Carry the pen over to the floor lamp on the left side of the couch
anns.task_desc: Carry a pen while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn around and walk past the television to the white table.
Take the pen near the keys closest to you.
Turn right then left and walk to the floor lamp next to the couch.
anns.task_desc: Get the pen from the table and go turn on the floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right once you are between the two chairs at the white table.
Pick up the pen in the center of the table.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the table, then turn left and walk to the lamp by the door.
Turn on the lamp beside the door.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp, across from the desk where you go the pen.
